# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tunge KILDE-assets — IKKE nødvendige for at køre spillet online.
# Holder GitHub-repoet lille (~26 MB i stedet for ~960 MB).
# Den spilbare version renderer kun fra:
#   assets/sprites/  ·  assets/backgrounds/  ·  assets/sounds/
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
assets/Blender/
assets/dele/
assets/turnaround/
assets/turnaround_lille_fjer/
assets/turnaround_rig/
assets/turnaround_stor_pels/

# Dyr-mappen: rå Blender-frames + 3D-kilder (688 MB). Den spilbare version
# renderer fra assets/sprites/. Når webp-pipelinen kobles ind i habitat.js,
# så un-ignore de FÆRDIGE frames, fx:  !assets/dyr/**/walk/**/*.webp
assets/dyr/

# Blender / 3D-kilder generelt
*.blend
*.blend1
*.glb
*.obj
*.mtl

